            "description": "TagInput — pixel-faithful Blueprint v6.15 tag input. Renders a list of removable Tag chips inside an input-group-styled container, with a ghost text input that grows to fill remaining space. Behavior: - Enter → add tag (split on separator) - Backspace on empty input → remove last tag - Paste with multiple values (addOnPaste=true) → split + add immediately - Blur (addOnBlur=true) → add current text - Click container → focus ghost input - Click × on tag → remove that tag",
